WEBVTT

00:12:26.368 --> 00:12:30.298
then there's no need
to build a bridge between you,

00:12:30.322 --> 00:12:32.082
because you've closed the chasm.

00:12:33.684 --> 00:12:37.493
Focus on that instead of your words,

00:12:39.021 --> 00:12:43.038
and it may be the most uplifting
conversation of their life.

00:12:44.568 --> 00:12:47.528
What could that do
for somebody you care about?

00:12:48.203 --> 00:12:50.528
What could it do for you?

00:12:51.181 --> 00:12:52.332
Thank you.

00:12:52.356 --> 00:12:57.277
(Applause)